CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

June 2, 2006

[Cite as 06/02/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-2722.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2006-1029. In re Disqualification of Martin.

This cause is pending before the court upon appellant’s notice of appeal from a decision under R.C. 2701.03. Whereas this court lacks jurisdiction to hear an appeal from proceedings under that statute,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that this cause is dismissed sua sponte.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
